      "review_summary": "The PR updates `extensions/nostr/src/nostr-profile.ts` to keep the per-relay profile publish timeout handle and clear it in a `finally` after the `Promise.race` settles.\n\nPR surface: Source +8. Total +8 across 1 file.\n\nReproducibility: yes. at source level: current main and `v2026.6.11` allocate an OpenClaw wrapper timeout and do not clear it when `pool.publish` wins the race. I did not run a live Nostr relay publish, so this is source-reproducible rather than run-reproduced.",
