      "target": {
        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix: clear timeout timer in Nostr profile relay publish loop",
        "body": "## What Problem This Solves\n\nFixes an issue where each Nostr relay publish would leave a dangling timer after `Promise.race` completed.\n\n## Why This Change Was Made\n\nWrap the per-relay `Promise.race` in `try/finally` that clears the timer handle.\n\n## User Impact\n\nNo user-visible change. Prevents a minor timer leak when publishing Nostr profiles.\n\n## Evidence\n\n```\nextensions/nostr/src/nostr-profile.test.ts\nTest Files  1 passed (1)\n     Tests  31 passed (31)\n[test] passed 1 Vitest shard in 12.31s\n```\n\nSame pattern as `src/node-host/with-timeout.ts:37-45`.",
